attributes.Long form description: The student disassembles a rolling cart, first removing the wheels, unscrews the top tray and removing it, unscrews the middle tray and removing it, unscrews the bottom tray and removing it, unscrews and disassembling the side of the bar, and finally disassembles the base frame.

The student disassembles the bottom tray of the rashult.
